Spellanza Baguma Muhenda (Ọktoba 30, 1978) bụ onye otu ndị omeiwu Uganda.
Ọ bụ onye nnọchi anya nwanyị nke Kyenjojo District na mpaghara Tooro na Western Uganda onye nwere njikọ na National Resistance Movement (NRM).
A mụrụ Spellanza Baguma Muhenda na 30 Ọktoba 1978 n'ezinụlọ ndị Katọlik
Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ Uganda Certificate of Education na Kyebambe Girls S.S
Ọ nọgidere na Kyebamba Girls S.s ebe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ ya Uganda Advanced Certificate of education na 1998
Ọ gara Mahadum Makerere nke afọ 2002 ebe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Bachelor of Education
Ọ gara maka agụmakwụkwọ ọzọ na Law Development Centre, Kampala ebe o nwetara asambodo na Law (Administrative Officers Law Course) n'afọ 2006
N'afọ 2008, ọ nwetara diplọma postgraduate ya na Public Administration and Management site na Uganda Management Institute.
Site na afọ 2000 ruo na afọ 2002, Spellanza Baguma Muhenda bụ onye na-enye ọzụzụ na Ruwoda
Ọ ghọrọ onye isi mmemme nke otu ndị ntorobịa Engabu za Tooro site na afọ 2002 - 2003
Ọ bụkwa onye isi nchịkwa maka ichebe ụmụaka-Kyenjojo site na afọ 2004 ruo na afọ 2006
Ọ ghọrọ onye ndụmọdụ maka Gọọmentị Obodo Kyenjojo site na afọ 2002 ruo na afọ 2006
Ọ bụ onye na-edeba aha distrikti maka National Resistance Movement na afọ 2006
Na Kyenjo District Local Government na 2006-2010, Baguma bụ Onye isi osote odeakwụkwọ
Ọ bụkwa osote odeakwụkwọ ukwu maka Gọọmentị Obodo Kyegegwa site na afọ 2010 ruo na afọ 2015
Ọ ghọrọ onye omeiwu na Nzukọ Ndị Omeiwu nke Uganda na afọ 2016 ruo taa.

Ọ bụkwa onye otu Kọmitii Akụnụba Gọọmentị Obodo ma bụrụkwa onye otu kọmitii na-ahụ maka Ọrụ Ọha na Gọọmenti Obodo. Ọ bụ osote onye isi oche nke Kọmitii Ahụike nke ndị omeiwu na 10th parliament nke Uganda na onye mmeri na nsogbu ahụike ọmụmụ mmekọahụ.
Ọ bụ onye isi oche nke Network for African Women Ministers and Parliamentarians (NAWMP) ugbu a.

O gosipụtara arịrịọ na-achọ ka gọọmentị tinye ụkpụrụ ndị dị mkpa ga-emetụta ndụ ndị na-eto eto. Ọ na-ekwupụta nchegbu mgbe niile banyere arụmọrụ nke ndị ọrụ ahụike distrikti. Ọ na-ekere òkè mgbe niile n'imeziwanye agụmakwụkwọ. O sonyere n'ịmepụta atụmatụ mkpuchi ahụike onwe onye.
